import React from 'react'
import About from './component/about/About'
import Experience from './component/about/Experience'
import Sevices from './component/about/Sevices'
import Brand from './component/about/Brand'
import Ourvalue from './component/about/Ourvalue'
import Updates from './component/about/Updates'

export default function Aboutus() {
  return (
    <>
        <About/>
        <Experience/>
        <Sevices/>
        <Brand/>
        <Ourvalue/>
        <Updates/>
    </>
  )
}
